  "original_title": "\u0daf\u0dd9\u0dc0\u0dd0\u0db1\u0dd2 \u200c\u0da7\u0dd9\u0dc3\u0dca\u0da7\u0dca \u0dad\u0dbb\u0d9c\u0dba\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0dbd\u0d82\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0da7 \u0d89\u0db1\u0dd2\u0db8\u0d9a \u0dc4\u0dcf \u0dbd\u0d9a\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dd4 39\u0d9a  \u0da2\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sri Lanka won by an innings and 39 runs in the second test match",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Sri Lankan team managed to win the second Test between the two countries by defeating the visiting Australia team by an innings and 39 runs. Accordingly, the two-match Test series ended 1-1.",
        "Australia, who batted first in the match, managed to score 364 runs. In response to that, the Sri Lankan team who played the innings scored 554 runs. The Sri Lankan team managed to restrict the Australian team to 151 runs who played their second innings.",
        "Dinesh Chandimal who scored a double century in this match was awarded as the hero of the tournament and Prabhat Jayasuriya who took 12 wickets in the debut match was awarded as the hero of the match."
      ],
